      "message": "I'm probably one of the last hold-outs that prefers abbreviations.  :-)  The less my eye has to take in, the more quickly I can grasp what the code is doing.  For me, long names make that much more difficult, because they tend to grab my eye's attention, rather than letting me see what the statement or code block, as a whole, is doing.",
